# Logistics Engineering Glossary

## Industrial Crating
Custom-built protective crate systems designed for transportation of machinery, commercial equipment, and export cargo.

## ISPM 15
International phytosanitary standard regulating heat-treated wood packaging materials used in global shipping.

## Container Stabilization
Process of securing cargo within freight containers to reduce movement during transportation.

## Dunnage
Protective material used to secure and cushion freight during transport.

## Intermodal Logistics
Transportation system involving multiple transportation modes including truck, rail, and ocean freight.

## Vapor Barrier Protection
Moisture-resistant wrapping system designed to protect cargo from humidity exposure.

## Freight Risk Mitigation
Engineering methods used to reduce cargo damage during transportation.
